comments.body:
@baude PTAL

I am mostly worried about (yet another) breaking change to existing users. @Luap99, as the cobra expert in team: Is it possible to add sub-commands as described here (i.e., `play-kube-{up,down}`) AND to main the current flags of `play-kube`?

Having written that, it seems like a recipe to create more confusion by mixing apples and oranges.  I sympathize with the suggestion but I am not convinced it's worth a breaking change.

@containers/podman-maintainers PTAL
